# 96. [只出现一次的数字](https://leetcode.cn/problems/single-number/)136-20260116

## 技巧：位运算

```python
class Solution:
    def singleNumber(self, nums: List[int]) -> int:
        ans = 0
        for n in nums :
            ans^=n
        return ans
```

# 97. [多数元素](https://leetcode.cn/problems/majority-element/)169-20260116

## 用on的空间

```python
class Solution:
    def majorityElement(self, nums: List[int]) -> int:
        mp = defaultdict(int)
        for n in nums :
            mp[n]+=1
        for k,v in mp.items() :
            if v > len(nums)/2 :
                return k
```

```python
class Solution:
    def majorityElement(self, nums: List[int]) -> int:
        nums.sort()
        return nums[(len(nums) - 1) // 2]
```

## 用o1的空间 随机找

```python
class Solution:
    def majorityElement(self, nums: List[int]) -> int:
        majority_count = len(nums) // 2
        while True:
            candidate = random.choice(nums)
            if sum(1 for elem in nums if elem == candidate) > majority_count:
                return candidate
```

## Boyer-Moore 投票算法

```python
class Solution:
    def majorityElement(self, nums: List[int]) -> int:
        count = 0
        candidate = None

        for num in nums:
            if count == 0:
                candidate = num
            count += (1 if num == candidate else -1)

        return candidate

